1965
02:32:07,505 --> 02:32:10,907
that have been so delinquent for so long and not getting repairs.

1966
02:32:11,767 --> 02:32:12,727
And that's not happening.

1967
02:32:13,268 --> 02:32:16,929
So I'd like to report back, you know, I don't know where the school committee is on this.

1968
02:32:17,830 --> 02:32:20,091
You know, I think they have an obligation to explain this.

1969
02:32:20,671 --> 02:32:36,218
