1975
02:33:27,036 --> 02:33:29,918
It defeats the whole purpose of a vocational school education.

1976
02:33:30,858 --> 02:33:33,960
So I'm going to make this in three counts, Mr. President.

1977
02:33:35,177 --> 02:33:37,419
